## EDGAR APIレスポンス例

SEC公式の submissions API のレスポンス例：

``` json
{
  "accessionNumber": "0000320193-24-000010",
  "form": "10-Q",
  "filingDate": "2024-02-02",
  "primaryDocument": "aapl-20231230.htm",
  "documents": [
    {
      "name": "aapl-20231230.htm",
      "type": "10-Q",
      "description": "Quarterly report"
    },
    {
      "name": "aapl-20231230.xml",
      "type": "EX-101.INS",
      "description": "XBRL instance document"
    }
  ]
}
```

利用上は以下のようにマッピング可能：

-   form → DisclosureType
-   documents\[\].拡張子 → FormatType
-   accessionNumber → docID

